<h3>Test Results</h3>
<p><strong>Prompt used:</strong> "The future of artificial intelligence lies not in replacing human creativity, but in amplifying it. We stand at the threshold of a new era." — narrated with professional broadcast tone</p>
<ul>
<li>Voice naturalness: 9.8/10 — indistinguishable from human</li>
<li>Generation time: ~3 seconds (5-second clip)</li>
<li>Emotional expression: 9.5/10 — pitch, pace, and tone variations</li>
<li>Language support: 9/10 — 30+ languages with native accents</li>
<li>Voice cloning accuracy: 9.5/10 — from 3-minute sample</li>
</ul>

